{"id": "nos034", "name": "Cam_ShadowSt_702_12_21", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "WAHHH... It's really pouring. Shoulda listened to mommy and brought an umbrella. The weather report here is as sucky as always! I'm starting to miss Node 08...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "Running"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma-chan said it was somewhere around here...?\n......!\nXenon...?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">It really is Xenon!</font> I finally found you... wah! My goddd! How come you are all black and blue!? You're getting soaked!\nLemme take a pic for Aroma-chan first...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "Takes Picture"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "You... What happened to you!? How did you end up like this!?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Y-Y-Y-You... You gotta go to the hospital! Let's go to Kyubo Medical Center? Nora will definitely help you for free! Ah, gotta tell everybody too.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Pulls hand"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Erghhh~~~com' on and get up! NEKO can't pull ya all alone!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "...Why aren't ya moving? Whatever! Getting soaked like this with all these cuts is no good! Let NEKO help you, huh? There's a pharmacy over there...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">... Leave me alone.</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... eh? What?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Leave me alone... go away...\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "NO WAY!! NEKO promised Aroma-chan and others that I'd find you!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... And then? You found me. Now leave.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "What the heck is that!? Nora needs your help with a lotta stuff over there. NEKO shouldn't couldn't and wouldn't just leave you here.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\nI... I can't do anything...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Whatta you mean? Xenon's amazing...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You don't understand, do you? All I see is the people around me getting caught up in terrible things... All because of me... ugh...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">It's not like that...</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Go away. It's not safe with me.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... Not safe? Well, well so what!? NEKO doesn't know what's going on with you, but I'm not just throwing you to the curb! NEKO knows you're upset about Sis Cherry... but so is everybody else! Point is, everybody's got to work together...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You done?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... eh?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I've always... hated your personality.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......!\nNEKO... <font size=\"1.6\">just wanted...</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "All you do is blabber on about what you want to talk about. Don't care about anyone else's feelings. You don't know anything, yet you put on this façade of understanding just to feel validated.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You just go on and on, so annoying. How old are you? An annoying brat who says the stupidest stuff. Everybody work together? Like what? Who is this \"everybody\" anyway? Didn't you run away from all that?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<i><font size=\"1.6\">... *sob*...</font></i>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You're clearly not of any use. No need to say that crap to me. I've heard enough of your voice. If you want to feel validated, go somewhere else. Or maybe go fish for compliments from your fans on the internet. I don't care, just go away...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "Slap"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "... You... big, dumb idiot... <font size=\"1.6\"><i>*sob*</i></font>... Fine, you can just rot here!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "Running"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "わわわ……ほんとに降ってきた！ママの言うとおり傘持ってきててよかったー\nやっぱこっちの天気システムダメダメじゃん！\nちょっとNode08に帰りたくなってきたかも……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aromaっちが言ってたのってたぶんここら辺だよね……\n……！\nXenon……？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">ほんとにXenonだ ！</font>\nやっと見つけた……\nうわ！えええ！ちょ！全身傷だらけじゃん！\nなんでそんな状態で雨にあたってるの！\nとりあえず写真を撮ってAromaっちに……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "写真"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "ねぇ……どうしたの？\nなんでそんなことになってるの！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "とっ……とととにかく病院！\n九芒医療に行こ？Noraならきっとタダで見てくれるから！\nあ、みんなにも報告しきゃ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "手を引く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "んんん～～！立ってよー！\nNEKO、Xenonを持ち上げるほど力持ちじゃないってば！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……動けないの？\nとにかく！傷口が雨に濡れるのはよくないよ！\nNEKOと一緒に来て？確かあっちに薬局が……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">……放っておいてくれ。</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……え？なに？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "放っておいてくれ……どっか行ってくれないか……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "そんなことできるわけないじゃん！\nNEKO、Aromaっちたちに絶対にXenonを見つけるって約束したんだから！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……それで？\n見つけただろ。じゃあな。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "だからどうしたのってば！\nNoraっちがXenonの助けを必要としてるの。\nそれに、こんな状態のXenonを放っておくなんてNEKOできないよ！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n……俺には……何もできない……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "なんで？Xenonはすごいよ……？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お前には分からないだろ？\n俺はみていることしかできない。\n身の回りの人たちがどんどん不幸に巻き込まれていくのを……それも、俺のせいで……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">そんなことない……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "行けよ。\n俺と一緒にいるのは危険だ。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……危険？\nなっ！そ！それが何！？\n確かに！Xenonに何があったのかNEKOには分からないよ！\nでも、だからこそXenonを一人にしておくなんてできない！\n……Cherryさんが、あんなことになって……Xenonが悲しんでるのはNEKOもわかるよ……\nでも！悲しいのはみんなも一緒なの！\n大事なのはこれからどうするかだよ。\nみんなで一緒に解決策を探して……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "言いたいことはそれで全部か？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……え？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "昔から……お前のその性格にはうんざりしてた。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！\nNEKOは……<font size=\"1.6\">ただ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "自分の話したいことばかりベラベラと……相手のことをほんの少しでも考えたことがあるか？\n何も知らないくせに、分かったふりをして同意を得ようとする。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "自分勝手で、周りに迷惑しかかけられない。\nいつまでも子供みたいに、意味の分からない話ばかりして。\nもう何歳だと思ってるんだ？\nみんなで一緒に解決策を考えるだと？\n「みんな」って誰だよ。お前は逃げ出したんだろ？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……っ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お前は何の役にも立たない。\nきれいごとばかり並べるな。\nお前の声にはうんざりだ。\n誰かにかまってもらいたいなら、よそでやってくれ。\nネット上にはお前をちやほやしてくれるファンが腐るほどいるだろ？\nならそっちで勝手に……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "巴掌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……Xenonの……バカ……<font size=\"1.6\">ひっく……</font>Xenonなんか……ここでいつまでもうじうじしてれば！？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇哇哇……真的下雨了，好險有聽媽媽的話帶傘。這邊的天氣系統果然還是那麼爛！有點想回 Node 08 了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 醬她們說的應該就是這附近吧……？\n……！\nXenon……？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">真的是 Xenon 啊！</font>總算找到你……哇！天吶！你怎麼全身都是傷！？還在這邊淋雨！\n先拍張照給 Aroma 醬……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "拍照"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "你……怎麼了？怎麼變成這樣！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "要要要……要快點去醫院才行！去九芒醫療吧？Nora 一定會免費幫你的！啊，也得通知大家。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯～～快點起來！NEKO 拉不動你啦！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……走不動嗎？總之！傷口這樣淋雨是不行的！NEKO 來幫你吧？旁邊有藥局……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">……別管我。</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……欸？啥？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別管我……走開……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那怎麼行！？NEKO 答應 Aroma 醬他們會找到你的！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……然後呢？妳找到了，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "到底怎麼了啦！？Nora 醬那邊好像很多需要你幫忙的地方，NEKO 不能這樣放著你不管。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n……我……什麼都做不到……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "怎麼會？Xenon 很厲害的……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳不會懂的吧？我只能不斷看著身邊的人被捲入不幸……因為我……唔……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">才不是這樣……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳走吧，跟我待在一起不安全。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……不安全？那、那又怎樣！？NEKO 不知道你怎麼了，但才不會把你一個人丟在這裡！NEKO 知道 Cherry 姐走了，你很消沉……但是大家也都一樣啊！重要的是，大家還是會一起想辦……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳說夠沒？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……咦？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我從以前……就很討厭妳這種個性。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！\nNEKO……<font size=\"1.6\">只是想……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "只會嘰哩呱啦地說著自己想講的事，完全不顧其他人的感受。什麼都不知道，卻裝作一副自己都懂的樣子來博取認同感。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我行我素，到處惹麻煩。都已經幾歲了？還像個小鬼一樣，講一些狗屁不通的話。大家會一起想辦法？想什麼辦法？那個「大家」又是誰？妳不就逃出來了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "明明一點用場都派不上，就不用在這裡說這些漂亮話，我受夠妳的聲音了。想刷存在感的話去別的地方，或上網找妳的粉絲討拍，隨便妳愛滾去……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "巴掌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……你這個……大白痴……<font size=\"1.6\">嗚……</font>就在這邊腐爛掉算了！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "흐에에엥...진짜 비 오네. 그래도 엄마 말대로 우산을 챙겨와서 다행이야. 이곳 날씨는 역시 여전히 글러먹었어! Node 08로 돌아가고 싶다...\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 짱이 말했던 곳이 이 근처인 것 같은데....?\n......! \nXenon......? \n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">진짜 Xenon이잖아! </font>\n드디어 찾았어......헉! 세상에! 왜 온몸이 상처투성이야!? 게다가 여기서 비까지 맞고 있고! 우선 사진을 찍어서 Aroma 짱에게......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "사진을 찍는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "대... 대체 무슨 일이야?\n꼴이 말이 아니잖아!\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "빠빠빠......빨리 병원에 가자! Kyubo 의료 센터로! Nora 짱이 분명 무료로 진료받을 수 있도록 손을 써줄 거야! 아 참! 우선 모두에게 연락을!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "손을 당긴다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "으으으으~ 빨리 일어나라구! NEKO 힘으로는 무리란 말이야!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......못 움직이겠어? 어쨌든! 이런 상처에 비까지 맞으면 진짜 위험하다구! NEKO랑 같이 가자, 응? 바로 옆에 약국이 있으니까......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">......신경 꺼.</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......응? 뭐라고?\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "신경 끄라고...... 비켜......\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "어떻게 그래!? NEKO는 널 찾는 걸 돕겠다고  Aroma 짱이랑 이미 약속까지 했단 말이야!\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......그래서? \n지금 찾았으니 이제 가 보라고.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "대체 왜 그러는데!? Nora 짱이랑 그쪽에 있는 친구들이 Xenon 도움을 필요로 하고 있단 말이야. 게다가 NEKO도 이런 상태의 Xenon을 그냥 내버려 두고 있을 순 없어!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n......내가 할 수 있는 건.....아무 것도 없어.......\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "무슨 말이야? Xenon이 얼마나 대단한데......\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이해 못 했어?\n나는 끊임없이 주위 사람들을 불행으로 몰고 갈 뿐이다...\n나 때문에.... 크윽....\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">꼭 그런 건 아니었잖아......</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "어서 가. \n나랑 있으면 안전하지 못하니까.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......안전하지 않다고? 그, 그게 어때서!? 네게 무슨 일이 있었는지는 NEKO도 잘 모르겠지만 그래도 Xenon을 이곳에 혼자 내버려 둘 수는 없다구! NEKO도 Cherry 언니가 그렇게 돼버려서... Xenon이 슬퍼한다는 거 알고 있어... 하지만 Xenon만 슬퍼하는 게 아니라 모두가 똑같이 슬퍼하고 있다구! 중요한 건, 다 함께 다시...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "아직도 할 말 남았나?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......어?\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "난 옛날부터......네 녀석의 그런 성격이 정말 싫었다.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......! \nNEKO는.... <font size=\"1.6\">그냥......</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그저 내뱉고 싶은 말이 있으면 멋대로 내뱉기나 하고 다른 사람 생각은 해보지도 않지. 아무것도 모르면서 자기는 이해한다고 말하며 다른 사람의 동의를 구하기나 하고 말이지.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "남의 말도 절대로 귀담아듣지 않고 아기들마냥 의미를 알 수 없는 말만 내뱉을 뿐이야. 다 함께라고? [함께]는 누구를 말하는 거지? 넌 거기서 도망 나왔잖아?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......흐흑......</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "넌 아무런 도움도 안 돼. 네 목소리는 이제 지긋지긋하니까 하고 싶은 말이 있으면 다른 곳에서 하든지 인터넷에서 멋대로 지껄이든지 해. 거긴 네 말에 공감해주는 팬들도 썩어날 테니. 이제 그만 꺼져라....\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "뺨을 때린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": ".....Xenon은......진짜 바보야......<font size=\"1.6\">흑......</font>여기서 죽어버리든 말든 맘대로 하라구!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "달려간다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇哇哇……真的下雨了，好險有聽媽媽的話帶傘。這邊的天氣系統果然還是那麼爛！有點想回 Node 08 了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 醬她們說的應該就是這附近吧……？\n……！\nXenon……？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">真的是 Xenon 啊！</font>總算找到你……哇！天吶！你怎麼全身都是傷！？還在這邊淋雨！\n先拍張照給 Aroma 醬……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "拍照"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "你……怎麼了？怎麼變成這樣！？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "要要要……要快點去醫院才行！去九芒醫療吧？Nora 一定會免費幫你的！啊，也得通知大家。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯～～快點起來！NEKO 拉不動你啦！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……走不動嗎？總之！傷口這樣淋雨是不行的！NEKO 來幫你吧？旁邊有藥局……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">……別管我。</font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……欸？啥？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "別管我……走開……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那怎麼行！？NEKO 答應 Aroma 醬他們會找到你的！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……然後呢？妳找到了，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "到底怎麼了啦！？Nora 醬那邊好像很多需要你幫忙的地方，NEKO 不能這樣放著你不管。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n……我……什麼都做不到……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "怎麼會？Xenon 很厲害的……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳不會懂的吧？我只能不斷看著身邊的人被捲入不幸……因為我……唔……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">才不是這樣……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳走吧，跟我待在一起不安全。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……不安全？那、那又怎樣！？NEKO 不知道你怎麼了，但才不會把你一個人丟在這裡！NEKO 知道 Cherry 姐走了，你很消沉……但是大家也都一樣啊！重要的是，大家還是會一起想辦……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳說夠沒？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……咦？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我從以前……就很討厭妳這種個性。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！\nNEKO……<font size=\"1.6\">只是想……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "只會嘰哩呱啦地說著自己想講的事，完全不顧其他人的感受。什麼都不知道，卻裝作一副自己都懂的樣子來博取認同感。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我行我素，到處惹麻煩。都已經幾歲了？還像個小鬼一樣，講一些狗屁不通的話。大家會一起想辦法？想什麼辦法？那個「大家」又是誰？妳不就逃出來了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "明明一點用場都派不上，就不用在這裡說這些漂亮話，我受夠妳的聲音了。想刷存在感的話去別的地方，或上網找妳的粉絲討拍，隨便妳愛滾去……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "巴掌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……你這個……大白痴……<font size=\"1.6\">嗚……</font>就在這邊腐爛掉算了！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_Rain"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "哇哇哇……真的下雨了，好险有听妈妈的话带伞。这边的天气系统果然还是那么烂！有点想回 Node 08 了……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 酱她们说的应该就是这附近吧……？\n……！\nXenon……？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Grass", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">真的是 Xenon 啊！ </font>总算找到你……哇！天呐！你怎么全身都是伤！ ？还在这边淋雨！\n先拍张照给 Aroma 酱……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "拍照"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "image", "attrs": ["nos3401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "你……怎么了？怎么变成这样！ ？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "要要要……要快点去医院才行！去九芒医疗吧？ Nora 一定会免费帮你的！啊，也得通知大家。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "嗯～～快点起来！ NEKO 拉不动你啦！\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……走不动吗？总之！伤口这样淋雨是不行的！ NEKO 来帮你吧？旁边有药局……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.2\">……别管我。 </font>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……欸？啥？\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "别管我……走开……\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "那怎么行！ ？ NEKO 答应 Aroma 酱他们会找到你的！\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……然后呢？妳找到了，走吧。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "到底怎么了啦！ ？ Nora 酱那边好像很多需要你帮忙的地方，NEKO 不能这样放着你不管。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n……我……什么都做不到……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "怎么会？ Xenon 很厉害的……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳不会懂的吧？我只能不断看着身边的人被卷入不幸……因为我……唔……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">才不是这样……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳走吧，跟我待在一起不安全。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……不安全？那、那又怎样！ ？ NEKO 不知道你怎么了，但才不会把你一个人丢在这里！ NEKO 知道 Cherry 姐走了，你很消沉……但是大家也都一样啊！重要的是，大家还是会一起想办……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳說够没？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……咦？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我从以前……就很讨厌妳这种个性。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……！\nNEKO……<font size=\"1.6\">只是想……</font>\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "只会叽哩呱啦地说着自己想讲的事，完全不顾其他人的感受。什么都不知道，却装作一副自己都懂的样子来博取认同感。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我行我素，到处惹麻烦。都已经几岁了？还像个小鬼一样，讲一些狗屁不通的话。大家会一起想办法？想什么办法？那个「大家」又是谁？妳不就逃出来了吗？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……呜……</font>\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "明明一点用场都派不上，就不用在这里说这些漂亮话，我受够妳的声音了。想刷存在感的话去别的地方，或上网找妳的粉丝讨拍，随便妳愛滚去……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Slap", "巴掌"], "content": ""}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！ ？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "……你这个……大白痴……<font size=\"1.6\">呜……</font>就在这边腐烂掉算了！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Run_Water", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}